==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: pak-choi
<hw>pak-choi</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An Asiatic plant (<spn>Brassica
rapa</spn> <varn>chinensis</varn>) grown for its cluster of edible white
stalks with dark green leaves.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bok choy, bok choi, pak choi, Chinese white cabbage,
<spn>Brassica rapa</spn> chinensis.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pakfong</ent>⟦br⟧
